# check the ports generally it will be listen to container port only
$ docker ps

# to specify por to listen for localhost
syntax:
docker run -d -p <localhost_port>:<container_port> --name c1 <img_name>

Usage:
$ docker run -d -p  80:3000 --name c1 hello


# now check the ports ,it will be listen to localhost & container port 
$ docker ps
